  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK513">
<l>aṉpaṟivu tēṟṟa mavāviṉmai yinnāṉku</l>
<l>naṉkuṭaiyāṉ kaṭṭē teḷivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let the choice (of a king) fall upon him who largely possesses these four things, love, knowledge, a clear mind and freedom from covetousness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
